CREATE OR REPLACE WAREHOUSE SECOND_WH
WITH
WAREHOUSE_SIZE = XSMALL
MIN_CLUSTER_COUNT  = 1
MAX_CLUSTER_COUNT  = 1
INITIALLY_SUSPENDED = TRUE
COMMENT = 'This is our second warehouse'


----------- IF the warehouse  get suspended if we want to use again resume the ware house  see below for syntax ----------
                      ----------  ALTER WAREHOUSE SECOND_WH RESUME ------------- 

----- IF WE WANT TO SUSPENDED USE ------------ALTER WAREHOUSE SECOND_WH SUSPEND 

--------CHANGE THE SIZE OF THE WARE HOUSE ----ALTER  WAREHOUSE  SECOND_WH SET WAREHOUSE_SIZE = XSMALL-------------

---------DROP -----
 DROP WAREHOUSE SECOND_WH
